e":"2018-05-01T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"連機都未有點知自己想要咩,淨係問邊間廠好都已經世界大戰，都唔知點答佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實應該拆開攝影台同攝影裝備/器材台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貼相又無討論，大家得過貼字同負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用家討論入面又變成買機買鏡邊到好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我E D真係咩都唔識又無錢玩太多鏡真係唔識點討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec05282f9aa6710d12191b57bc24f9b28b7380d4","tid":648563,"uid":18753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"756859218ab30602958df9334dc7cec3107ca325","tid":648563,"uid":63119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T04:45:14.000Z","msg":"我諗幾難，癲佬唔洗多，幾個已經夠搞衰呢度。一係就屌牌子，一係就攞陳年事件loop，根本完全無養份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"癲佬一個都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入到去又比佢變成戰場，離晒題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b6b99c5b17543838d57da36a3fc388c03a1923","tid":648563,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"171b8254cfca718d655c27ca2d8ae968798e3b52","tid":648563,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"682d590ccb55cf402e06faef45f0265316f79496","tid":648563,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edcdb93218cf2a131e8ec8213dc473f1533a2f11","tid":648563,"uid":7026,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:18:04.000Z","msg":"兩登攝台都俾貓蛇整彎左啦<br />\n加上香港玩相機風氣好差<br />\n驚個境、驚隻雀俾人燒左<br />\n啲攝影圈子圍威餵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T04:18:31.000Z","msg":"香港影相風氣真係好差<br />\n啲呀叔識少少就好似好威咁<br />\n每次出街影相都一定有人挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T04:26:45.000Z","msg":"以前N記班叔父係<br />\n我唔係用N記 <br />\n俾佢地講到我其實應該即場去死<br />\n如果肯賣家剷入N記跟阿叔學野都仲有D機會咁<br />\n<br />\n宜家？ <img src=\"/assets/fac